com.facebook.buck.cxx

Class PreInclude

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.rules.AbstractBuildRule
      • com.facebook.buck.rules.AbstractBuildRuleWithDeclaredAndExtraDeps
        • com.facebook.buck.rules.NoopBuildRuleWithDeclaredAndExtraDeps
          • com.facebook.buck.cxx.PreInclude
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasDeclaredAndExtraDeps, SupportsInputBasedRuleKey, BuildRule, CxxPreprocessorDep, NativeLinkable, Comparable<BuildRule>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CxxPrecompiledHeaderTemplate, CxxPrefixHeader

    public abstract class PreInclude
extends NoopBuildRuleWithDeclaredAndExtraDeps
implements NativeLinkable, CxxPreprocessorDep
    Represents a precompilable header file, along with dependencies.

    Rules which depend on this will inherit this rule's of dependencies. For example if a given rule R uses a precompiled header rule P, then all of P's deps will get merged into R's deps list.

      • requirePrecompiledHeader

        protected com.facebook.buck.cxx.CxxPrecompiledHeader requirePrecompiledHeader(boolean canPrecompile,
                                                                              com.facebook.buck.cxx.PreprocessorDelegate preprocessorDelegate,
                                                                              CxxPlatform cxxPlatform,

                                                                              DepsBuilder depsBuilder,
                                                                              UnflavoredBuildTarget templateTarget,
                                                                              com.google.common.collect.ImmutableSortedSet<Flavor> flavors,
                                                                              ActionGraphBuilder graphBuilder)
        Look up or build a precompiled header build rule which this build rule is requesting.

        This method will first try to determine whether a matching PCH was already created; if so, it will be reused. This is done by searching the cache in the ActionGraphBuilder owned by this class. If this ends up building a new instance of CxxPrecompiledHeader, it will be added to the graphBuilder cache.
